'''納吉·亞當'''（{{lang-hu|Nagy Ádám}}，{{bd|1995年|6月17日}}）是一名[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]職業足球運動員，在場上的位置是中場。現效力於[[意乙|意乙]]球隊[[比薩1909足球會|比薩]]，曾效力[[費倫斯華路士體育會|費倫斯華路士體育會]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://int.soccerway.com/matches/2015/05/16/hungary/nb-i/paksi-se/ferencvarosi-torna-club/1767749/|title=Paks 0-1 Ferencváros|date=16 May 2015|publisher=Soccerway.com|access-date=2016-06-20|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031155345/https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2015/05/16/hungary/nb-i/paksi-se/ferencvarosi-torna-club/1767749/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/memberassociations/news/newsid=2348538.html|title=Ferencváros crowned Hungarian champions|date=2 April 2016|publisher=[[UEFA.com|UEFA.com]]|access-date=2016-06-20|archive-date=2020-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200706031430/https://www.uefa.com/memberassociations/news/newsid=2348538.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[匈牙利國家足球隊|匈牙利國家足球隊]]成員<ref>[http://www.national-football-teams.com/player/60461/Adam_Nagy.html] {{Wayback|url=http://www.national-football-teams.com/player/60461/Adam_Nagy.html |date=20201031154145 }} at National-Football-Teams.com</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://int.soccerway.com/matches/2015/09/07/europe/european-championship-qualification/northern-ireland/hungary/1653338/|title=Northern Ireland 1-1 Hungary|date=7 September 2015|publisher=Soccerway.com|access-date=2016-06-20|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107092301/https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2015/09/07/europe/european-championship-qualification/northern-ireland/hungary/1653338/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並且入選了匈牙利2016年歐洲國家盃參賽名單。

